OL,3,CFour arrests and another charged after
OL,4,CDoncaster man fatally stabbed
OL,6,FA total of four people have been
OL,7,Farrested, and another has been charged
OL,8,Fwith murder, following the death of a
OL,9,Fman from Doncaster.
OL,11,FWayne Solomon, 57, was found at
OL,12,FGalsworthy Close with serious injuries
OL,13,Fon Wednesday 24 June.
OL,15,FHe was taken to hospital where he died.
OL,17,FWayne's family said that he "wasn't
OL,18,Fjust loved, he was cherished.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
