OL,3,CFour arrests and another charged after
OL,4,CDoncaster man fatally stabbed
OL,6,FA man, 52, was arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder and another man, 28, was
OL,8,Farrested on Monday 29 June also on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,11,FTwo women, 51 and 45, have been
OL,12,Farrested on suspicion of assisting an
OL,13,Foffender.
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector, Ben Wood,
OL,16,Fsaid: "Our investigation into Wayne's
OL,17,Fdeath is continuing at pace and we are
OL,18,Fcontinuing to appeal for information
OL,19,Fwhich can assist or enquiries.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
